That is such pure bullshit. What it is saying is that people like me (who happens to be far more liberal than conservative) do not want to be at the mercy of a crazed criminal looking to score some cash to supply his heroine habit. It means I don't want to be waiting 10-20 minutes for an officer to arrive when someone is breaking my door down in a psychotic rage. It means that if it comes between me dying so that some criminal can have my money or a criminal dying because he attacked a citizen who has the means to defend himself, I want to be the last one standing.<br>
<br>
I don't want to be at the mercy of criminals depending only on the police who might not even be in the area. And even if they are in the area, minimum response is going to be 5 minutes... 5 minutes! Take a watch and time out 5 minutes and then ask yourself how much can happen in that time.<br>
<br>
My family depends on me to protect them and I take that responsibility seriously. I am not going to place my family's safety completely in the hands of law enforcement. If they are on scene when the shit hits the fan - great, I'll let them handle it. If they are not, then I damn well am going to have other options... it's only common sense. <p><br>
